OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear spells
OL,6,Fand a few showers at first this
OL,7,Fevening. Turning cloudier with
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain overnight, these may
OL,9,Fbe heavy at times. Strong winds,
OL,10,Fespecially near coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA mixed day of bright spells
OL,13,Fand blustery showers, best of the dry,
OL,14,Fbright spells in the north and east.
OL,15,FStrong south to southwest winds which
OL,16,Fmay reach gale force.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
