OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FSunny
OL,6,Fspells and a few showers on Monday.
OL,7,FDry with sunny spells Tuesday. Mostly
OL,8,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain on
OL,9,FWednesday. Winds light Monday then
OL,10,Fbreezy on Tuesday and Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
